This button is inspired by [url=http://custombuttons.sourceforge.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=3749]a post/request by [b]steve.marks59[/b][/url]. It allows to toggle the enabled state of any GreaseMonkey/Scriptish script and reflect that state on the button's image.

