[b][size=150]Compatibility[/size][/b]
Tested and working on Firefox Stable/Dev. Edition, SeaMonkey and Palemoon.
[b][color=#FF0000]Not compatible with Nightly nor Windows Vista[/color][/b]

[b][size=150]Usage[/size][/b]
[list]
[*] Options are changed by editing the Initialization tab of this button.
[*] Edit the [b]scriptName[/b] variable for the exact name of the user script you want this button to handle.
[*] Edit the [b]enabledImage[/b] and/or [b]disabledImage[/b] variables to change the images representing the enabled/disabled state of the user script.[/list]

[b][size=150]Button clicks[/size][/b]
[list]
[*] [b]Left click:[/b] Toggle script status\t\n" +
[*] [b]Middle or Control + Left click:[/b] Open script options\t\n" +
[*] [b]Control + Shift + Left click:[/b] Edit script\t\n\n" +[/list]

